1. Compile and install trento using the source file trento-master.zip
official instruction: http://qcd.phy.duke.edu/trento/installation.html

2. Generate events
Example configuration files are in "config" directory
$> $(TRENTO_INSTALL_DIR)/bin/trento -c conf_pAu.conf

This will generate text files of the 2D profile

3. Convert Trento text files to histograms
config/Convert2D.C

4. Generate SONIC input text files with a scale factor
Note: If there are tuned initial 2D profile from MC-Glauber, 
	a scale factor can be calculated by comparing mean value of
	integral of 2D profiles, tuned MC-Glauber and untuned Trento
